{"tid":1764482,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"iPhone 12 系列將改用 Samsung 製 OLED 屏幕 用上獨家柔性屏幕技術","createTime":"2019-12-01T06:51:45.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-02T02:20:32.000Z","uid":341649,"like":5,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"9c32532c8396b95f9e644a5e86ce4b3152ed5976","tid":1764482,"uid":341649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-01T06:51:45.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://ezone.ulifestyle.com.hk/article/2508583/iPhone%2012%20%E7%B3%BB%E5%88%97%E5%B0%87%E6%94%B9%E7%94%A8%20Samsung%20%E8%A3%BD%20OLED%20%E5%B1%8F%E5%B9%95%20%E7%94%A8%E4%B8%8A%E7%8D%A8%E5%AE%B6%E6%9F%94%E6%80%A7%E5%B1%8F%E5%B9%95%E6%8A%80%E8%A1%93\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fezone.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Farticle%2F2508583%2FiPhone%252012%2520%25E7%25B3%25BB%25E5%2588%2597%25E5%25B0%2587%25E6%2594%25B9%25E7%2594%25A8%2520Samsung%2520%25E8%25A3%25BD%2520OLED%2520%25E5%25B1%258F%25E5%25B9%2595%2520%25E7%2594%25A8%25E4%25B8%258A%25E7%258D%25A8%25E5%25AE%25B6%25E6%259F%2594%25E6%2580%25A7%25E5%25B1%258F%25E5%25B9%2595%25E6%258A%2580%25E8%25A1%2593&d=HsMqQMGMM0KOGi%2FJd%2BN0BytC6Bij9UJRoh6Gg3PlEes%3D&h=7069bd09\" target=\"_blank\">https://ezone.ulifestyle.com.hk/article/2508583/iPhone%2012%20%E7%B3%BB%E5%88%97%E5%B0%87%E6%94%B9%E7%94%A8%20Samsung%20%E8%A3%BD%20OLED%20%E5%B1%8F%E5%B9%95%20%E7%94%A8%E4%B8%8A%E7%8D%A8%E5%AE%B6%E6%9F%94%E6%80%A7%E5%B1%8F%E5%B9%95%E6%8A%80%E8%A1%93</a><br />\n<br />\n近日韓國有報導指，來年的 iPhone 12 系列將全面改用 OLED 屏幕，而且全部由韓國廠商提供，當中 iPhone 12 Pro 和 iPhone 12 Pro Max 的 OLED 屏幕更會由 Samsung 獨家代理，用上 Samsung 自家柔性屏幕技術，以降低成本，屏幕亦可變得更薄。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">iPhone 屏將由韓國生產</span><br />\n<br />\n根據韓國媒體報導，有消息指 Apple 來年的 iPhone 將全面改用 OLED 屏幕，而且全部都會由韓國廠商提供，當中的 6.1 吋型號（預計為 iPhone 12）的 OLED 屏幕會由 Samsung 和 LG Display 提供，而 5.4 吋型號（預計為 iPhone 12 Pro）和 6.7 吋型號（預計為 iPhone 12 Pro Max）的 OLED 屏幕則會由 Samsung 成為獨家代理，用上 Samsung 自家研發的 YOUM On-Cell Touch AMOLED（Y-OCTA）屏幕，而現時 Samsung 大部分手機都是採用這款屏幕。 Samsung 自行研發的 Y-OCTA 屏幕採用內置觸控功能，無需再額外使用觸控薄膜，能夠使屏幕比起一般 OLED 屏幕更薄，同時又能節省成本，所以成功吸引 iPhone 轉用。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n一般 OLED 屏幕（左），Samsung 獨家的 Y-OCTA 屏幕（右）。<br />\n<br />\n另外，早前亦有報導指 Apple 曾向中國京東方購買 OLED 屏幕進行測試，但直至現時仍未有消息，可能是屏幕未能滿足 Apple 的要求，亦有可能是 Apple 避免屏幕因中美貿易戰而影響成本。除此之外，網上亦有傳聞指 Apple 來年會推出 iPhone SE2 或 5G 版 iPhone，不過直至還有未屏幕訂單資料流出。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nSource：<a href=\"http://gizchina.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fgizchina.com&d=HsMqQMGMM0KOGi%2FJd%2BN0BytC6Bij9UJRoh6Gg3PlEes%3D&h=4afe467f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">gizchina.com</a>"},{"pid":"f1ca6ae05fd78293807d427edf7112e6c365710e","tid":1764482,"uid":341649,"like":19,"dislike":1,"score":18,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-01T06:52:12.000Z","msg":"蘋果唔用京東方oled 可喜可賀可喜可賀"},{"pid":"1a040b03be49e9a9966157025708a09ab54cc151","tid":1764482,"uid":109923,"like":17,"dislike":2,"score":15,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-01T06:54:33.000Z","msg":"嗰班話用OLED傷眼嘅，好快啲買多幾部11旁身啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ad38b10f02afc59705d9ccddcaacb809ec289e98","tid":1764482,"uid":213877,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-01T06:54:41.000Z","msg":"IPHONE 13呢？"},{"pid":"813e803200e849ed2f23bd2dec17213b5aacf758","tid":1764482,"uid":9387,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"quote":{"pid":"1a040b03be49e9a9966157025708a09ab54cc151","tid":1764482,"uid":109923,"like":17,"dislike":2,"score":15,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-01T06:54:33.000Z","msg":"嗰班話用OLED傷眼嘅，好快啲買多幾部11旁身啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-01T07:09:22.000Z","msg":"仲可以永續考古iPhone 8"},{"pid":"f309fcc973b926d5e168baf032868bcf0a8c452c","tid":1764482,"uid":12628,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-01T07:09:39.000Z","msg":"X開始已經係三叔mon啦，so exciting"},{"pid":"b2952bee5a043481a2744a49fbacb4404af82408","tid":1764482,"uid":12628,"like":1,"dislike":5,"score":-4,"quote":{"pid":"813e803200e849ed2f23bd2dec17213b5aacf758","tid":1764482,"uid":9387